2.)
 For Loop- the loop executes if the condition is true and terminates when the condition is false.
 If statement- the statement executes if it’s true and skips the statement if it’s false.
 While loop- the loop checks the statement to continue to make sure it is true and keeps repeating as long as the expression remains true. 

